  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Authentication
    Handles the top-level authentication choices for the CLI, allowing users to log in, register as a company representative, or exit the system.
    CR_SPAM_INTERN
    Scripted scenario that logs in as a company representative and creates multiple internship submissions in one run.
    CR_SPAM_REGISTRATION
    Scripted scenario that registers multiple company representatives in succession.
    CRIntensiveScenarioMain
    Replays a comprehensive company representative journey that exercises filtering, listing, reviewing applications, toggling visibility, and creating new internships.
    LoginController
    Coordinates credential collection and routes users to the appropriate home page based on their role.
    Main
    Launches the Internship Placement Management System from the command line.
    RegistrationController
    Collects company representative registration details and records them for staff approval.
    StaffIntensiveScenarioMain
    Drives an end-to-end staff scenario that exercises filters, approvals, reports, and password updates.
    TestScenarioMain
    Exercises student flows by replaying canned input through the existing CLI controllers.
